---

<section id="notes" class="relative py-24 overflow-hidden bg-slate-50">
  <!-- Subtle Background Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none">
    <svg width="100%" height="100%">
      <pattern id="grid" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
        <path d="M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" />
      </pattern>
      <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid)" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">
        University <span class="text-[var(--accent-color)]">Material</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-[var(--accent-color)] rounded-full mb-8"></div>
      
      <div class="max-w-3xl p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/20 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Notes from the course of Aritificial Intelligence of Ionian University (2024).
          Covering essential concepts in Logic, search strategies like BFS/DFS, 
          competitive AI with MiniMax, 
          optimization via Hill Climbing, 
          and various Classification methodologies.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-10">
          Diclaimer: The author makes no guarantees regarding the completeness, accuracy, or suitability of the materials for any specific purpose.
The use of the content is entirely at the userâ€™s own risk.
        </p>

        <a href="/ai-notes.pdf" download="ai-notes.pdf" class="inline-flex px-10 py-5 bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl hover:bg-[var(--accent-color)] transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-[var(--accent-color)]/25 items-center gap-3 group">
            Access Notes & Algorithms
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">
                <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
                <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
            </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #notes {
    --accent-color: #22A7F0;
  }

  .backdrop-blur-xl {
    backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
  }
</style>
